dditionally, the game showcases state-of-the-art technology designed to help individuals deal with landslides. &lt;em>It is also presented in the poster session of IEEE VIS 2023.&lt;/em>
For more details, please find at &lt;a href="https://slope-aoe.hkust.edu.hk/home">https://slope-aoe.hkust.edu.hk/home&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>ArtMirror</title><link>https://wtong2017.github.io/projects/artmirror/</link><pubDate>Fri, 03 Feb 2023 22:08:21 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wtong2017.github.io/projects/artmirror/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/metaartmirror/artmirror">&lt;strong>Art Mirror&lt;/strong>&lt;/a> is a VR soundstage for teachers and students to emulate cinematography lighting in virtual scenarios. Lighting education is a foundational component of cinematography education. However, many art schools do not have expensive soundstages for traditional cinematography lessons. Thus, migrating physical setups to virtual experiences is a potential solution driven by metaverse initiatives. &lt;em>This project is also presented in IEEE VRW 2023, ACM MM 2023.&lt;/em>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Pvis2023datavideo</title><link>https://wtong2017.github.io/publications/pvis2023datavideo/</link><pubDate>Fri, 03 Feb 2023 21:55:35 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wtong2017.github.io/publications/pvis2023datavideo/</guid><description/></item><item><title>AsymCollabVis</title><link>https://wtong2017.github.io/publications/asymcollabvis/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Jan 2023 23:08:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wtong2017.github.io/publications/asymcollabvis/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Vrw2023artmirror</title><link>https://wtong2017.github.io/publications/vrw2023artmirror/</link><pubDate>Tue, 17 Jan 2023 21:46:03 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wtong2017.github.io/publications/vrw2023artmirror/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Vr23CondAccept</title><link>https://wtong2017.github.io/news/vr2023/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 Jan 2023 12:36:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wtong2017.github.io/news/vr2023/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Vis2022conf</title><link>https://wtong2017.github.io/news/vis2022/</